Go right for Minimal kills looking at the PvP Pit area that is <br>
there is like 2-3 mobs there that may or may not see invis. im not to sure on that but you can kill them or not kill them i think there is only 1 that can see invis there just Drop into pit after you have killed the 3 mobs on the Right side of the PvP pit in the ( Stands/ Veiwing area ) then Drop Down into the Pit go to the Left Door in the pit and there is the mob that Drops the SoM + 1 other mob there with him 5-8 kills + entrance mobs all together a in and out deal this is the Best Fastest and easyest way to Get SoM that i Know of and can be done with a group less then 4 55+ min. 60's would be Preferable but Doable with 55+ <br>
